amily: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&bull;<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Lihat di navigator, jika tidak tampil, klik menu Window &gt;&gt; Navigator</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&bull;<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Untuk Panel kedua, tambahkan Table, dan Button&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&bull;<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Ubah teks pada button menjadi Hapus</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&bull;<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Ubah konten tabel dengan cara klik kanan, pilih <strong>Table Contents</strong> &hellip;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&bull;<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Pilih tab Rows, ubah nilai Count menjadi 0</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&bull;<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Pilih tab Columns, ubah nilai Count menjadi 7, ganti Title , hilangkan checklist pada Editable</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&bull;<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Ubah lebar (width) sesuai kebutuhan (satuan pixel), Pref. untuk lebar standar, Min. untuk lebar minimal, Max. untuk lebar maksimal</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&bull;<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]-->Misalnya untuk UTS, UAS, dan Grade, ubah nilai ketiga width (Pref., Min., dan Max.) menjadi 60, yang lain disesuaikan (atau tetap default)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\